            <description><![CDATA[<p>Release date: 2026-06-27</p>
<p>This update improves upgrade flows and recovery when automatic folder
processing is interrupted.</p>
<h2 id="new">New</h2>
<h2 id="improvements">Improvements</h2>
<h2 id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed paid upgrades from trials getting stuck.</strong>
Upgrading from a trial to a paid Managed plan now completes more
reliably and refreshes credits sooner.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed Self-Managed upgrade sheets closing
unexpectedly.</strong> Upgrading from a Self-Managed trial now keeps the
upgrade sheet open when your trial state refreshes.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed onboarding license-step loops.</strong> The onboarding
flow no longer keeps reopening the same license step while license
status updates are settling.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed interrupted Watch Folder scans.</strong> NameQuick now
recovers abandoned folder catalog scans after restart and clears stalled
processing state more safely, so automatic folder work and content
search can recover instead of staying stuck.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed repeat retries for files that need review.</strong>
Unsupported, unreadable, or too-large files are now treated as file
issues to review instead of being retried as temporary processing
failures.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
